{"tid":2413092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方直擊： 放寬措施後首個午市　不少市民未用「安心出行」　邊等位邊填表","createTime":"2021-02-18T12:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T15:21:19.000Z","uid":196321,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4667c3ae41b60e74f42f3f1b928a4329c6827271","tid":2413092,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:16:07.000Z","msg":"放寬措施後首個午市　不少市民未用「安心出行」　邊等位邊填表<br />\n<br />\n政府今日（18 日）起有條件放寬防疫措施，容許食肆延長堂食時間至晚上 10 點，最多 4 人坐一枱，前提是食肆須確保客人使用「安心出行」或登記資料。<br />\n<br />\n午市時間，《東方》記者在港島各區觀察。其中，銅鑼灣「大渣哥茶記」有職員指示輪候食客填寫資料卡，須填上姓名、聯絡電話及入座時間，入座前將資料卡投入收集箱。<br />\n<br />\n灣仔食肆「開餐」亦有提供表格予食客登記，填妥後對摺放入密封收集箱。餐廳強調，資料按政府要求儲存 31 日後，會由負責人親手銷毁。食客鄧小姐認為手寫登記都方便，較可保障私穩；她又說不會裝「安心出行」，因不想留資料給政府，形容「白癡先會裝安心出行」。<br />\n<br />\n至於在炮台山的「時代冰室」，店員表示如果不想掃「安心出行」二維碼，必須留下個人資料，登記紙由職員負責收集，之後對摺投入箱中。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道<br />\nOncc. 政府澄清外賣毋須「安心出行」掃碼　推翻陳肇始上周說法<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3docOxF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3docOxF&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Hr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=0d8b1e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3docOxF</a><br />\n<br />\nOncc.【安心出行？】Mos Burger 宣佈繼續停晚市堂食<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3arQv8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3arQv8d&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Hr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=bd103033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3arQv8d</a>"},{"pid":"969413d9c3ae9f0e3833057ee3fc60a0b8bf8866","tid":2413092,"uid":57582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"佢去黃店問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96c124d20d779c1dd40f3acad61a95460d873c3","tid":2413092,"uid":18477,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>屌你老母白粉仲乜鳩做stalker mon住黃店呀<br />\n死怨婦</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444c8817f9507f3bff5334d3c2d933ee92c853ef","tid":2413092,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"969413d9c3ae9f0e3833057ee3fc60a0b8bf8866","tid":2413092,"uid":57582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"佢去黃店問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"特登，答乜都死<br />\n答唔要求客人scan ，姐係犯法<br />\n答會要求客人scan，不過可以留資料，又有啲人出嚟屌黃店屈服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc4c302aaa43037d5e0d805056b10f59005f0bd","tid":2413092,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"如果我話。。。即係如果。。。呢篇野係立場寫架呢？"},{"pid":"d127107f2c2680273bf4b57951a12efcc4eefc65","tid":2413092,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"三間黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc5a21e63a5ebb5a7751f1949df8db69d940e4a","tid":2413092,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc4c302aaa43037d5e0d805056b10f59005f0bd","tid":2413092,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"如果我話。。。即係如果。。。呢篇野係立場寫架呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"反而合理啲<br />\n東方問黃店個記者short撚左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d75b9ee8c214282ebb5bbda9d1d77826c7a55d","tid":2413092,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"